title: RIL to announce Q1 earnings on July 18
description: Mukesh Ambani-owned Reliance Industries (RIL) will announce its June quarter earning on Friday, July 18. The company will also hold an analyst meet, post the board meeting to discuss the financial result for the quarter ended June 30, 2025.
